@startuml
title UC09 - Consultar Extrato da Conta

' Configuração visual melhorada
hide footbox
autoactivate off
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #374151
    LifeLineBorderColor #9CA3AF
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #F9FAFB
    ParticipantBorderColor #374151
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #E8F5FF
    ActorBorderColor #374151
    ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    DatabaseBorderColor #374151
    DatabaseBackgroundColor #F3E8FF
    BoxBorderColor #9CA3AF
    BoxBackgroundColor #FAFAFA
    GroupBorderColor #9CA3AF
    GroupBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    ActivationBorderColor #111827
    ActivationBackgroundColor #CFE3FF
    ParticipantPadding 28
    BoxPadding 10
    MessageAlign center
}
skinparam maxMessageSize 70

actor Aluno as A
boundary "Perfil do Aluno
Next.js" as Front
control "AlunoController
Micronaut" as AlunoCtrl
control "TransacaoController
Micronaut" as TransCtrl
control "TransacaoRepository" as TransRepo
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

A -> Front: Acessa perfil do aluno
activate Front
Front -> AlunoCtrl: GET /alunos/{id}
activate AlunoCtrl
AlunoCtrl -> DB: SELECT aluno WHERE id = ?
activate DB
DB --> AlunoCtrl: Dados do aluno
deactivate DB
AlunoCtrl --> Front: AlunoResponse
deactivate AlunoCtrl

Front -> TransCtrl: GET /transacoes/aluno/{id}
activate TransCtrl
TransCtrl -> TransRepo: findByDestinatarioId(alunoId)
activate TransRepo
TransRepo -> DB: SELECT transacoes recebidas
activate DB
DB --> TransRepo: Lista de transações
deactivate DB
TransRepo --> TransCtrl: List<Transacao>
deactivate TransRepo
TransCtrl --> Front: ExtratoResponse[]
deactivate TransCtrl

Front -> Front: Renderiza saldo e histórico
Front --> A: Exibe extrato da conta
deactivate Front
@enduml
